#What does Perl stand for?

Perl is a backronym = Practical Extraction and Report Language or Pathologically Eclectic Rubbish Lister

Perl with capital refers to the language, perl with lowercase to the interpreter.

CPAN - Comprehensive Perl Archive Network

Perl is a "free-form" language, whitespaces are insignificant.

See perldoc perlstyle for styleguides (recommendations).